# Blog content and weekly automation

When editing **`posts/*.md`**, **`content/blog_topics.json`**, or **`content/blog_style.md`**, or when adding screenshots under **`blog/assets/`**, follow [`CONTRIBUTING_BLOG.md`](../../CONTRIBUTING_BLOG.md) and [`AGENTS.md`](../../AGENTS.md).

## Images

- Store screenshots in **`blog/assets/`** as optimized **`.webp`** files.
- Embed only with **site-root** Markdown: `![alt](/blog/assets/filename.webp)`. Relative `../assets/` paths are invalid and break [`scripts/build_blog.py`](../../scripts/build_blog.py).
- **`scripts/generate_blog_post.py`** picks the **next unused** asset (not already referenced in `posts/*.md`), sends it to Gemini with **vision**, and requires **exactly one** `/blog/assets/...` embed per draft.

## Automation

Weekly draft PR: [`.github/workflows/generate-blog-post.yml`](../../.github/workflows/generate-blog-post.yml). Rebuild static output with `npm run build:blog` after changing post sources.

Run `npm run test:blog` after changing blog generation/build rules. It covers Markdown image rendering, one-image validation, asset rotation, and preserving `blog/assets/`.
